metadata.name: f.ace #1
metadata.description:
A uniquely detailed style drawing inspiration from Picasso and other Cubism artists. Deep, carved and flowing wrinkles surround fractalized components of a face misshapen by futility.

The color choices are stark against the flat chalkboard like background, grounding the pieces in a state of nostalgic embrace that saves the viewer from the sometimes uncomfortable shaky linework constructing the faces that make up these pieces.
